subSubSection.paragraph:
Adult description.
Parsons (
1943
) provided an updated revision of LeConte’s (
1878
) original description. Although rudimentary line drawings of the mouthparts and male genitalia were provided, little detail on species level characters was given and female genitalia were not described. The following is a more complete and modern description of the species.

